{"id":150497,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/东盟峰会忧虑全球粮价上涨/","date":"2011-05-07T12:00:19Z","modified":"2011-05-07T12:00:19Z","title":"东盟峰会忧虑全球粮价上涨","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅加达</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周六（</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>7</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）开幕的本年度东南亚国家联盟峰会警告粮价上涨可能带来社会后果。峰会东道主、印尼总统苏西洛在开幕讲话中表示，应对全球粮食和能源价格上涨</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">提高警觉</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，必须采取对应措施，避免使价格上涨危及人民的生活。他指出，高涨的粮价使减少贫困人数的努力更为困难。东盟目前有</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个成员国，其中既包括石油资源丰富的文莱和高科技国家新加坡，也包括柬埔寨、老挝以及缅甸等穷国。本年度东盟峰会也将讨论至</span><span>2015</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年建成共同经济区的计划以及打击地区人口走私犯罪的问题。泰国和柬埔寨之间的边境冲突也是此次峰会的议题。数星期以来，这两个邻国之间发生激烈边境武装冲突，导致</span><span>18</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人丧生。印尼总统苏西洛在开幕讲话中就此表示，东盟应有能力创造一个外交和对话的平台，以实现共同和平。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15057818%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E4%B8%9C%E7%9B%9F%E5%B3%B0%E4%BC%9A%E5%BF%A7%E8%99%91%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%B2%AE%E4%BB%B7%E4%B8%8A%E6%B6%A8\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}